biography: Larissa is a Data Scientist working in Heidelberg. With university degrees in Political Science and Data Science, she combines ethical and business views on NLP projects. Besides that, she cares about AI in Science Fiction, Bullet Journaling, and bringing Roundnet to the Olympic Games.
